<p>When running my application on my Apple TV a white glow is added to my <code>UILabel</code> and <code>UIView</code>. Running my application on the simulator produces the results I expect, no glow. I suspected it was the <code>tint</code> property adding this white glow, but setting the <code>tint</code> property to <code>Clear Color</code> has not resolved my issue.</p>  <p><strong>Device</strong> (White glow):</p>  <p><a href="http://i.stack.imgur.com/QaPaL.jpg" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://i.stack.imgur.com/QaPaL.jpg" alt="enter image description here"></a></p>  <p><strong>Simulator</strong> (Expected results, no glow):</p>  <p><a href="http://i.stack.imgur.com/cbozz.png" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://i.stack.imgur.com/cbozz.png" alt="enter image description here"></a></p>